</tr>
<tr>
<td>2</td>
<td><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif">Fairness.</span> No one should get preferential treatment before the law, and no one is above the law. (Lawful)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>3</td>
<td><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif">Freedom.</span> Tyrants must not be allowed to oppress the people. (Chaotic)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>4</td>
<td><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif">Might.</span> If I become strong, I can take what I want — what I deserve. (Evil)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>5</td>
<td><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif">Sincerity.</span> There’s no good in pretending to be something I’m not. (Neutral)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>6</td>
<td><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif">Destiny.</span> Nothing and no one can steer me away from my higher calling. (Any)</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
