</tr>
<tr>
<td>2</td>
<td><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif">Responsibility. </span>It is my duty to respect the authority of those above me, just as those below me must respect mine. (Lawful)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>3</td>
<td><span class="Sans-Serif-Character-Styles_Bold-Sans-Serif">Independence.</span> I must prove that I can handle myself without the coddling of my family. (Chaotic)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>4</td>
